rom multiple friends, frenemies, and representatives, she is now quietly aw=
aiting the results of her employer=E2=80=99s investigation. The salient que=
stion for Haskell and Vox Media chief executive <b>Jim Bankoff</b>, of cour=
se, is whether her relationship with R.F.K. influenced any of her coverage=
=E2=80=94including, most notably, her memorable July <u><a href=3D"https://=
email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dTRWpOOXVkUER=
